msgstr "Activar funciones de Wikipedia (requiere Internet)"

#: settings-schema.json
msgid "Wikipedia language"
msgstr "Idioma de Wikipedia"

#: settings-schema.json
msgid "Show notable events on this day"
msgstr "Mostrar eventos notables de este día"

